strings:
<voice_0x0100171B><se_def>Prince Charmles: Honestly! Where has the Princess got to?
What could possibly be taking her so long!?

<voice_0x0100171D><se_def>Prince Charmles: What do you think you're doing!?
Are you trying to ruin my wedding!?

<voice_0x0100171E><se_def>Prince Charmles: I won't stand for it! Guards!
Get rid of him at once!
<voice_0x0100171F><se_def>*: Excuse me for the interruption Your Majesty, Lords, ladies and gentlemen. I, I have an urgent communiqué for the King.

<voice_0x01001721><se_def>Prince Charmles: What is it, Father?
Tell me at once!

<voice_0x01001722><se_low>King Clavius: It seems the bride...
Princess Medea has disappeared.
<voice_0x01001724><se_def>Prince Charmles: I don't believe it...! Well...she must have been kidnapped! It's the only explanation!

<voice_0x01001726><se_def>Prince Charmles: ...It was you!
This is all your doing!
<voice_0x01001727><se_def>Prince Charmles: He was jealous, so he kidnapped the Princess!
<voice_0x0100172B><se_low>Morrie: You lay the fingers onto my amico on top of my dead body!
<voice_0x0100172C><se_low>Morrie: Go, ragazzo! Leave this to me.
